    metaDescription: "Understand the critical difference between GDV and market value in property finance. Learn how each affects your loan amount and why lenders assess both.",
    excerpt: "GDV and market value are two distinct concepts that directly affect how much you can borrow. This guide clarifies the difference and explains how lenders use each figure in their credit assessment.",
