    metaDescription: "Received a low valuation on your development scheme? Learn the formal process for challenging it, what evidence you need, and when to instruct a second opinion.",
    excerpt: "A down-valuation can derail your development finance application. This guide explains the formal challenge process, the evidence required, and practical strategies for achieving a revised figure.",
    category: "valuations",
    datePublished: "2026-02-09",
